text: Rolf Erling Andersen (3 July 1947 – 7 August 2021) was a Norwegian politician. He was a member of the Labour Party. He was a member of the Norwegian Parliament from 1997 until 2005. Andersen died on 7 August 2021 at the age of 74.Rolf Erling Andersen (74) er død ==References== Category:Norwegian politicians Category:1947 births Category:2021 deaths
